query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cves (
            id TEXT PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL,
            source_identifier TEXT,
            published TEXT,
            last_modified TEXT,
            vuln_status TEXT,
            description_en TEXT,
            cvssv2_base_score REAL,
            cvssv2_vector TEXT,
            cvssv3_base_score REAL,
            cvssv3_vector TEXT,
            cpes TEXT,
            "references" TEXT, 
            weaknesses TEXT 
        );
